{"tid":2071741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：將向本港學生進行國安立法重要意義的宣傳教育","createTime":"2020-06-20T05:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T05:48:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"00ba4d5fcde8a2e8039aff473daab7a5dcc45045","tid":2071741,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄接受中央電視台訪問時說，將會因應港區國安法立法，向本港學生進行廣泛的宣傳教育，讓他們成為知法守法的青年人。<br />\n<br />\n他說會向學生介紹立法意義，希望讓學生知道國家安全對香港的穩定，帶來甚麼積極的作用，對香港將來的發展有甚麼帶動作用。他說香港學生都是國家的一部分，要令他們明白國家安全對他們來說都是一種責任和義務。"},{"pid":"33ea4aadf03d9be1148a639c5f58022da07cdbcb","tid":2071741,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1314830&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=5fa7865e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1314830</a>"},{"pid":"de95bb92a6b6abb1f05d862ba2d857e045c08111","tid":2071741,"uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"將政治帶入校園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a840d1af1daa83e5b728684149c57eee6b4d769","tid":2071741,"uid":129913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"呢個係Sydney香港人嘅組織<br />\n由舊年612開始喺澳洲搞左唔同嘅遊行同活動聲援我哋香港，佢哋今次邀請咗幾位澳洲議員，記者爆爆。曾健超同頭條新聞嘅曾志豪上緊個直播<br />\n。佢哋會輪流發言。討論關於對香港嘅睇法。<br />\n希望大家可以睇吓！<br />\n喺呢度特別多謝NSW HongKongers<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nswhongkongers/videos/265450087883352/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnswhongkongers%2Fvideos%2F265450087883352%2F&d=WBYYCruE%2BO8aOQq6cZO2w1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=7f2f85e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nswhongkongers/videos/265450087883352/</a> <br />\n有時間睇吓，幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42651e32f88adb356b5291373af19309ee9c44dc","tid":2071741,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:17:16.000Z","msg":"Say no to CCP!"},{"pid":"232e3390c35c63d0061ee6c43d169fb3832b7289","tid":2071741,"uid":255105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"咁局長你個澳洲讀書既仔又係咪「國家的一部分」？"},{"pid":"51b33d1412b9cd61dff0384b150ca682fbb50cbf","tid":2071741,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"我已經準備好拎住毛語錄鬥地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d立啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97282b8614f5c846be7c7a1dc15269eb709914cb","tid":2071741,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9393b35047f6b2cab9ed15f3d86a17f46e5702e1","tid":2071741,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"佢兩個仔唔番香港上國民教育??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988d97fa31a8036b52dd3108884530fa24bfacff","tid":2071741,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"呢班狗官自己都唔知國安法為何物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「港版國安法」加辣　林鄭索「草案文本」被北京婉拒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2071480\" data-auto-link ta